Program: Outlook
Title: I was an Arms Dealer's 'Pleasure Wife'
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p057l39c
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 11 Jul 2017
Former model Jill Dodd spoke to Jo Fidgen about joining the harem of Saudi arms dealer Adnan Khashoggi, one of the richest men in the world with powerful political connections. Jill retrained as a fashion designer and went on to found the global fashion brand Roxy. By day Chilean Roberto Antezana, works as a technician at an observatory in Santiago, but in his free time he loves to take photos of the stars, the ones in the sky, that is. Dr Lynne Jones is a British psychiatrist who has spent most of the last three decades helping people with mental illness in some of the poorest and most devastated parts of the world. Image: Jill Dodd Credit: Margot Moritz Show less